==================== Input ====================
// Pins the "trailing `//` comments don't count toward print width" divergence
// (see AGENTS.md "Known divergences"): Prettier counts the comment and breaks
// the value (`fade(\n  @white,\n  4%\n); // ...`); ours keeps the value flat.
@background-color-light: fade(@white, 4%); // background of header and selected item
@background-color-base: fade(@white, 8%); // short one stays put

==================== Output ====================
------------------
{ printWidth: 80 }
------------------
